Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:39.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0250,,#03 變革的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:48.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對外交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 居然有幸遇上你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為處女座的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是難逃感情主義的命運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是因為沒有放出發光粒子才被找到的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是後者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被壓制了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會被這麼巨大的傢伙擊中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為見面禮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先收下一塊碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 光束刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ビームサーベル（Beem Saber）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公元2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私設武裝組織「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣佈根除全世界紛爭 採取武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介入印度南部錫蘭島的民族紛爭一役後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震驚世界的Gundam Meister又接到了新的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是神對人類實施的制裁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是將世界引向變革的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個無法預測的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損失了來復槍 逃不了寫檢討
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次戰鬥中獲得的Gundam數據資料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算賠一架Flag都能有找零
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許能從接觸時附著的塗料追尋到蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來還真是年輕啊 天人的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對話過嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的動作上能看出感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Flag是什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:31.04,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}JNN 本社
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和當地特派員聯絡上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多小都行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加入Gundam的圖片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」沒有發佈聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分鐘內發佈特報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下條新聞是現場直播
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3小時內人革聯主席就會發表正式聲明 空出時間段來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 娟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21世紀後期出現的絕世發明大王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽能發電系統基礎理論的倡導者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少公開露面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有姓名被後世傳頌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他創建「天人」的話就倒可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論在技術還是資金方面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼過了兩百餘年 他們又開始行動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格家族的血緣 在他那代就完全斷絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:34.43,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}AEU 諜報機關本部 長官室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的資產去向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的紀錄上完全沒記載
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕被做過手腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21世紀的保安全系統幾乎形同虛設
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃得還真周到嘛 「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官 您認為他們的武裝介入會持續下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如是我的話會那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為議會報告準備好資料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有托辭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:04.49,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}人革聯 軌道升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通天柱交通公社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘通天柱E237次班機的旅客 請前往A12號口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這好勝的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你掛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告書已經上交Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後我也去看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞 天上方面就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們進入下一項任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服從命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會有不安因素
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說真的能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用軌道升降機將機體帶回天上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按計劃 把機體混雜在衛星開發用的材料中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要重量一質 完成搬運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的檢查可以無視 特別是在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是個盲點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說到我們的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在沒有Gundam的情況下 普特萊馬奧斯的活動時間會被很大程度限制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有4個太陽爐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把機密掛在嘴上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞的班機出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同天柱交通公社穿梭車 E277次班機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按預定時間 於14時18分 格林尼治標準時間5點32分發車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於14時18分 格林尼治標準時間5點32分發車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向天上的線路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算能回去了 地面真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點懷念休假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趁熱打鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一次兩次行動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界是不會承認我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多時了 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深有體會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 司令在等著您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前我想去趟錫蘭島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只相信自己親眼所見的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令也會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 屬下陪您一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:42.48,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}UNION MSWAD 本部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來只是視察AEU新型機體竟然搞出這麼多事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為有研究價值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面似乎也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因目擊過Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人有調動命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對Gundam」調查隊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新設立的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式名稱很快會由司令部決定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷夫·艾佛曼教授 由他擔任技術主任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說明上頭有足夠重視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉漢姆·艾卡中尉 畢利·片桐技術顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到轉屬「對Gundam」調查隊的調動命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你預料到事情會如此發展了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有萬能到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然隱約感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些命中注定的東西罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛爾蘭島的阿爾斯特地區是恐怖活動多發性地區
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是零星發生 但持續了將近四個世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說起源於天主教和新教這兩個基督教的不同流派之間的對立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩者的分歧還並不僅限於此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的報告以研究北愛爾蘭島的對立圖表為主題…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 又要交報告了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是工學部的說 為什麼還一定要上歷史課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的技術革新\N將以維持軌道升降機和開發殖民衛星（space colony）為中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和各國的技術人員進行交流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對歷史觀進行培養也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 老師在一開始不就說過了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂… 多虧了它 我才能有機會留學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面得感謝它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年後留學就要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 突然說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶… 沙慈你考慮過將來的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朦朦朧朧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之中有我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朦朦朧朧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 等下… 路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子 真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就應該追上來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是軟飲料麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推薦這裏的自製雞尾酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是未成年人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這真是失禮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三次任務即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要是有興趣的話 建議準備三台監視器哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢… 那可真令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拭目以待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偷看麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:10.23,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}錫蘭島內 人革聯 駐軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有什麼發現了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是瑟爾蓋中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請作一下說明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是MS的轟炸用可選部件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材質是E碳素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是最新素材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在構造上並未確認到任何新技術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載的導彈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 根據對殘留物質的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是300公斤級別的誘導型導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提 目前並沒有開發這種類型的國家或廠商
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是自行獨立開發的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從機體所受的衝擊度來看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為Gundam的輸出功率大概是Flag的6倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它到底裝了怎樣的引擎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸出功率自不用說 那種機動性更為驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根據戰鬥數據確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現那種機動性的果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是從Gundam的機體周圍散發出了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光粒子般的物質
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這證言能夠接受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷達和傳感器都沒捕捉到就是因為這個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種特殊粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了隱形性能之外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用在機體制御上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能用於火器上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷夫·艾佛曼教授
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個恐怖的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有領先我們幾十年的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天人的犯罪聲明中登場的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史人物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字倒是聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是太陽能發電系統的提倡者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報部似乎正在沿著這條線索追蹤Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深究也沒有結果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個部件也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能展示出來的技術都是人家用過不要了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的話 真想弄一架來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為Gundam的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 也希望您能對這架機體做進一步調整
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對機師的負擔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以無視
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 麻煩將期限控制在一周內
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真是個強人所難的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不稍微強硬一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是無法泡到Gundam的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經沉迷了無法自拔了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 總共有兩處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩處？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時行動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南非
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕 是要武力干涉礦物資源開採權所引起的內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:04.49,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}南非地域 礦物資源開採地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得像恃強凌弱似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點解除武裝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了 逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是學聰明點了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一架在塔利比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏能去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打心底就不喜歡毒品之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他們能把毒品全部燒光的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反而要支持Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒品?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算消滅紛爭之源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:14:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}南美地域\N塔利比亞上空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開迴旋行動已經過了30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 現在開始進入作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標達成率97%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這類小事 隨時肯干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三架出現在錫蘭島？這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在第七駐屯地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能用的Tieren嗎 我要出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校您是要親自去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只相信親眼所見之事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怪物嗎 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 繼續介入紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打！ 打！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好… 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一階段 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然扔掉了火器？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在試探我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要根除戰爭的覺悟 就讓我來見識見識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你的人頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額 想要門兒都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拿你的髒手碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達匯合地點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 已確認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著艦準備開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對接誘導系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集裝箱打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連動系統良好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著艦完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue的GN drive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與普特萊瑪奧斯的連接作業開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue到托勒密號的能量傳輸準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是天上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利結束了哦
